data.description: Welcome to this fantastic four-level split home, perfectly situated on a spacious lot in a highly desirable location. As you enter, you'll appreciate the convenience of the attached two-stall garage, offering not only ample storage but also direct access into the heart of the home. The well-designed kitchen boasts a generous center island, seamlessly connecting to the open dining and living areas, with easy access to the backyard patio for outdoor enjoyment. Headed to the upper level, you'll find three comfortably sized bedrooms and a nicely sized bathroom. The lower level is a cozy haven with a charming gas fireplace, brand new flooring, and an ideal office space setup. Additionally, this level features a ¾ bathroom equipped with laundry facilities, adding to the home's practicality. The lowest level houses the mechanical room, offering ample storage potential and future finishing possibilities for those looking to customize their space. This four-level split home is waiting for you!
